The '''Commerce Council''' operated within the government of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] and was part of the [[Senate Council]]. The Council was charged with regulating commerce throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] within the borders of each respective government. During the [[Black Fleet Crisis]], [[Dall Thara Dru]] was Chair of the Commerce Council. [[Cal Omas]] promised [[Cola Quis]] the Chair of the Commerce Council in exchange for supporting his [[New Republic Presidential election, 28 ABY|election]] to the post of [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]].

